<Layout
	title="About QANT Strategic Investments"
	description="Our Technical Core & Expertise"
	pubDate={new Date('April 16 2026')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		QANT Strategic Investments L.L.C-FZ is a specialized technology firm focused on high-frequency 
		environments and complex process optimization. We bridge the gap between advanced financial 
		logic and high-performance engineering.
	</p>

	<h3>Engineering Excellence</h3>
	<p>
		Our development team operates across the full stack, utilizing a rigorous approach to software 
		architecture. We specialize in low-latency systems and scalable enterprise solutions using:
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Low-Level & Systems:</strong> C, C++, Rust (Performance-critical modules)</li>
			<li><strong>Enterprise Logic:</strong> Java, C#</li>
			<li><strong>Agile & Web:</strong> JavaScript, Python, Full-Stack Frontend/Backend Integration</li>
		</ul>
	</p>

	<h3>Machine Learning & Quantitative Systems</h3>
	<p>
		We design and deploy <strong>Quantitative (QANT) Systems</strong> specifically engineered for 
		real-time execution via the Interactive Brokers (IBKR) API. Our focus lies in:
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Predictive Modeling:</strong> Implementing Machine Learning algorithms for pattern recognition.</li>
			<li><strong>Automated Optimization:</strong> Continuous self-developing systems that learn from daily market data.</li>
			<li><strong>Crisis Management:</strong> Proprietary modules like "Gamma-Hunter" for strategic option-chain scanning.</li>
		</ul>
	</p>

	<h3>Process Analytics</h3>
	<p>
		Beyond code, we provide deep-dive analytical audits. We specialize in the optimization of 
		complex business processes, utilizing AI-driven data classification to enhance operational 
		intelligence and decision-making speed.
	</p>
</Layout>
